* added dot matrix display SSD1306 device support.
* added partial sensor ECG ADAS1000 device support (work in progress).
* added fuel gauge MAX1720x active/hibernate.
* fuel gauge MAX1726x I2C 7 bit addresses bug fixed.
* extended MEMS LIS2DW12 configuration (interrupt active pin polarity).

