Version 1.3.2 [2019/03/11]
--------------------------
* for ARM platform, "Release" build configuration compiler optimization moved from -O3 to -Os (for size).
* PN7120 bus device moved to PN71x0 (added compatibility with PN7150 chip).
* PN71x0 bus device disabled (commented out) "CARDEMU_SUPPORT" support.
* added "write/read buffer" in "tommRoCHwBus" layer (targer is for I2C bus).
* added "lowPowerEnter/lowPowerExit" in "tommRoCHwBus" layer.
* refactor of "tommRoCHwCommNFCNDEF" layer.
* refactor of "tommRoCHwDevicesCommSubGHzRFM69HW" bus device.
* added "MMA8452Q" MEMS bus device.
* refactoring of library version (define moved to "tommRoCHwVersion.h" file).

+ libs
------
    * NfcLibrary V1.3.

+ source
--------
    * removed "tommRoCHwBusNotGuarded" layer for little reduction of layer binary size.
    * general little refactoring of some library bus devices.
    * some little bug fixed on "tommRoCHwDevicesMEMSConv" layer.

+ template
----------
    * generic little refactor for code size.
    * added bus "lowPowerEnter/lowPowerExit" functionality for ARM platform.
    * little refactor of I2C/SPI/UART template.

+ test
